dataLineage.statement:
Admin 4 layer was downloaded from the OCHA COD Registry. It was then analyzed by ITOS for errors. Those errors were corrected and then the layer was sent back to UNOCHA as a feature class within a file geodatabase.
The following errors were found and fixed by ITOS:
1. Created and populated a reference name field. 2. Admin 4 name field values changed to proper case. 3. Admin 0 values changed from "Mli" to "ML". 4. Admin 3 p-code field had its values repopulated with complete p-codes provided by the IMO. 5. Admin 4 p-codes were rebuilt with complete admin 3 p-codes. 6. Created and populated name and p-code fields for admin 1 and 2 values. 7. Fixed geometry errors concerning gaps and overlaps.
